## Predictive Modeling of Glucose Levels in Diabetic Patients

-   Conducted statistical analysis using a dataset from the National Institute of Diabetes and Digestive and Kidney Diseases to examine how factors of body influence blood glucose levels.

-   Selected the best model that best predict Glucose Levels based on diagnostic plots and significance testing.
